    tmp = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.74 - v2 + 0.60)) + wp.abs((v0 + 0.92 - tmp + 0.83)))
    v2 = 0.92
    v1 = (0.06 * (wp.sin(tmp + 0.20) * (v0 + 0.93 + v0 + 0.35)))
    data[tid] = v0
